{
  "stem": "443.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I asked, I kept on asking, till I found another man.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The only way we recognized each other, we used to call each other [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The word [NON-ENGLISH] means you're a Jew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "In other words, you're my-- my own.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You're a brother.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so I asked him, what do you do here?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Where do you go here?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He says, there's one place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He told me address.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And that's where all the refugees gather.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "When you get there, you sign in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There are books.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And you sign in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "In every book that there is, put your name down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "If someone is looking for someone, or if you are looking for someone, look-- go through the books.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You'll see who is alive, who survived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So I put my name in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There was a man next to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He saw my name, Deutsch.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So he says, well, I know a Deutsch.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I says, who do you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Says he knows a lady by the name Adieu Deutsch.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Adieu Deutsch, first, I thought was my sister.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Meanwhile, I found out it was my first cousin, my uncle's daughter.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So where do you go?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Where-- where is she?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "She is in the camp in Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "See, Bergen-Belsen was a camp for-- for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a camp where they kept the military, the soldiers, the officers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had regular barracks, good barracks, good buildings.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the people from the old barracks moved into these barracks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my-- my cousin, she was in one of the rooms with five other girls.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But how do you get there?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no trains.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no cars.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was no trucks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The only way you had communications over there is bicycles.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] It just so happened that I knew how to use a bicycle.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
